WEBVTT

00:00.140 --> 00:02.007
_

00:02.117 --> 00:05.378
- All these people?
- All these people.

00:05.403 --> 00:06.746
And you're prepared to go public?

00:06.772 --> 00:09.379
- Cath Hardacre, witness to the truth.
- Right, step away.

00:09.405 --> 00:12.127
Shocking neglect of patients
at Sheffield Alderman Hospital.

00:12.153 --> 00:15.215
- What do you want me to do?
- Go call a doctor.

00:15.241 --> 00:17.288
I need to be heard
but I need to do it the right way.

00:17.314 --> 00:19.621
These allegations of negligence
have all been

00:19.647 --> 00:21.436
fully investigated by the trust.

00:21.462 --> 00:22.911
You're suspended.

00:24.481 --> 00:25.929
You're a great nurse.

00:25.955 --> 00:27.523
I can't believe they did that to you.

00:27.549 --> 00:31.059
Anything you ever need from me
and it's yours.

00:36.614 --> 00:39.677
Dad, I think I'm going to be a doctor.

00:40.366 --> 00:42.274
It's a chance for a much better life.

00:42.911 --> 00:46.201
This is a bloody great CV.
Why the hell are you here?

00:46.227 --> 00:50.233
I was married, there were problems.
I needed a change.

00:53.167 --> 00:55.492
I want to see her.
I've got a right to see her.

00:55.571 --> 00:57.796
Always try and look
after you young doctors

00:57.822 --> 00:59.612
when you move in, right enough.

01:00.098 --> 01:03.213
Data leaks, theft of property,
drug fraud.

01:03.239 --> 01:06.855
If you see anything suspicious,
report it.

01:07.201 --> 01:08.403
So, who am I?

01:08.444 --> 01:11.863
You're Ally, but I can
still call you Mummy.

01:12.211 --> 01:13.500
Dr Sutton?

01:13.794 --> 01:15.848
Andrew Brenner. Andy.

01:22.287 --> 01:24.306
So when was the last time
you ran a trauma?

01:30.951 --> 01:34.163
<i>Hi, Cath, this is Sam Kelly
from The Sheffield Express.</i>

01:34.383 --> 01:37.600
<i>I hope this is the right number.
I need to speak to you urgently.</i>

